# Audit Specs Must Stay Normative

When updating files under `specs/features/*/*audit-spec*.md`:

- Do not leave stale point-in-time status snapshots (e.g. old FAIL counters/checklists) after fixes land.
- Keep spec text normative and current; move temporal progress tracking to `specs/features/*/REVIEW.md`.
- Every audit finding marked resolved must reference at least one regression test file.
- Before marking an audit spec as PASS, verify the mapped focused tests run and pass.
